message: Yusaku: "There's no need to be so scared."
Yusaku: "Even the aftercare is fully prepared."
Chihiro: "Ah... no... it's too fast... slower..."
Yusaku: "What happened to Mr. Sakamoto on the first floor?"
Yusaku: "What about your neighbor, Mr. Saito?"
Chihiro: "He... divorced, and now only his wife is there..."
Yusaku: "What about the fat man who noticed you in the city?"
Chihiro: "Ah... since then... hah... hah... I haven't seen him..."
Yusaku: "What about the liquor store and the cleaning shop?"
Chihiro: "Both of them are really scared... when I go to the store, they hide in the back... so the wives always take their place..."
Chihiro: "He's very kind to me. He helps me decline newspaper subscriptions, and when I need to dispose of heavy trash..."
Chihiro: "I... I don't want semen anymore... I want to feel good with... with your penis... with your penis, Manager..."
